  <original-body>This patch includes two commits:

1) An extract-class refactoring of the dynamic finder name matching code from AR::Base. The matching code is now in DynamicFinderMatch, which simplifies things a bit.

2) The ability to add a bang to a simple find_by dynamic finder.  Person.find_by_name!(&quot;Josh&quot;) will raise a RecordNotFound error instead of returning nil.

Both commits include appropriate tests.</original-body>
